              <p class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">14 Weeks • Full-time</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Learn to build complete web applications from front-end to back-end. Master modern frameworks, databases, and deployment strategies used by top tech companies.
          </p>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">What You'll Learn:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
