            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Cybersecurity</h3>
              <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold">18 Weeks • Full-time</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Protect digital assets and infrastructure from cyber threats. Learn ethical hacking, security analysis, and incident response to become a cybersecurity professional.
          </p>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">What You'll Learn:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center">
